+=== Calling a processor as an endpoint
+
+Calling a processor as an endpoint from a route such as:
+
+[source,java]
+----
+from("jms:cheese")
+  .to("myProcessor");
+----
+
+Is no longer supported. Instead either use the bean component to call the processor or use `process`:
+
+[source,java]
+----
+from("jms:cheese")
+  .to("bean:myProcessor");
+----
+
+Or
+
+[source,java]
+----
+from("jms:cheese")
+  .process("myProcessor");
+----
+
